# Backend Scoped Rule

- Keep backend changes isolated from frontend/API concerns unless required.
- Before changing deployment scripts, verify backend runtime assumptions.
- For API surface changes, update contracts and compatibility notes.
- Prefer incremental refactors that preserve existing behavior.
